   (a) use, install, and run the Software internally to deploy, manage, and
       operate containers for the purpose of delivering Your Product to End
       Users, where revenue from End Users is primarily attributable to Your
       Product and not to access to or use of the Software's deployment-
       management capabilities;

   (b) modify the Software for your internal use as described in (a);

   (c) make copies reasonably necessary for backup and internal operations
       under (a)–(b).

